  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-user ticketing system with role-based access (clients, collaborators, staff)",
    "Event ticket generation and inventory management with seat mapping",
    "Order processing with multi-currency and payment gateway support (Stripe, Mercantil, Banco de Venezuela)",
    "Integration with Seats.io for venue seating and chart management",
    "Access control system for event entry and exit tracking",
    "Virtual and offline ticket office capabilities with synchronization",
    "Digital billing and invoicing with TFHKA integration",
    "Real-time analytics and indicators for sales, revenue, and platform metrics",
    "Mobile app API for ticket viewing, transfer, and QR code access",
    "Conciliation system for transaction reconciliation with banks"
  ],
